g":"寫咁大篇野都唔知佢個wish list做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edec170fb341c0d26305686500114df2d020ef4","tid":1303741,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a6b4ae7efd742e4b37d71d3ca22a5bb2ab1df6","tid":1303741,"uid":106027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"寫咁大篇野都唔知佢個wish list做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講，今次steam活動話送game，送邊隻就睇你放咩係願望清單度，咁d人咪del晒其他平game留返貴game搏抽中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}